---
title: Cumin-Spiced Steak with Scallion Dressing and Spinach Couscous Salad
description: Cumin is one of our favorite spices to cook with because it has tons of deep, earthy flavor without any heat. Its effect is subtle yet unmistakable, elevating steak to new heights in this recipe. It also loves a good contrast: here, it embraces a pucker-y scallion dressing with lemon and the veggie flavors of spinach and red pepper tossed with couscous.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w17-r2-classic-fbd9efe2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w17-r2-classic-daf0d6a2.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
